      "title": "Announcement by the Ministry of External Affairs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Diplomatic Affairs Division of the Ministry of External Affairs has announced that due to the current situation in the country, it will provide services to the public only on Mondays, Wednesdays and Fridays till July 10.",
        "This also applies to regional embassies in Jaffna, Matara, Kandy, Trincomalee and Kurunegala."
